<div>
    <h2>
        We love what we do, and how we do it.</h2>
    <p>
        We work with natural materials and search the world for the softest fabrics we can
        find. We choose our production partners with great care and take our decisions on
        the design, colors, safety, and perfect fit rather seriously.
    </p>
</div>
